Catering in Englewood, FL
Catering for Weddings, Parties & Corporate Events
On Premise Events:
We have a semi-private patio area to host your wedding reception, holiday party, retirement party, birthday party or a friendly fun private gathering. We can accommodate 50-60 people. We offer buffet style service or limited menu sit down dining for your meal options.
Off Premise Events:
We are available to cater your special occasion at another location on Manasota Key or in the Englewood, Florida area..
Please contact Ashley Dignam, our Catering/Event Manager, at
ashley@manasotakeygroup.com
or
941.468.1415
.
Ashley Dignam, Catering/Event Manager
